'''Zaafrane''' ({{lang-ar|<U+0632><U+0639><U+0641><U+0631><U+0627><U+0646>}}) is a small desert oasis village in central [[Tunisia]]. It is located at around {{coord|33|26|17|N|8|55|5|E}} and is the gateway to the [[Grand Eastern Erg]] desert. It is the centre for the traditionally nomadic [[Adhara people]].

